                  <msItem>
                     <p>
                        <placeName key="place_108012">Daventry</placeName> and <placeName>Drayton</placeName>, The Symond Holding.

   <persName>
                           <forename>William</forename> of <surname>D<supplied>aventry</supplied>
                           </surname>
                        </persName> son of the late <persName>
                           <forename>John</forename> of <surname>D<supplied>aventry</supplied>
                           </surname>, kt.</persName>, grants to <persName>
                           <forename>Robert</forename> 
                           <surname>Simond</surname> of <placeName role="person" key="place_108012">D<supplied>aventry</supplied>
                           </placeName>
                        </persName> and <persName nymRef="Simond">
                           <forename>Henry</forename> his son</persName> 4 acres of arable land in <placeName key="place_108012">D<supplied>aventry</supplied>
                        </placeName> and <placeName key="place_108013">Drayton</placeName>, viz. in the south field of D<supplied>aventry</supplied> 1 acre lying together in <placeName key="place_108152">D<supplied>aventry</supplied> Mawelond</placeName> by the land late of <persName>
                           <forename>John</forename> le <surname>whelwryghte</surname>
                        </persName>; ½ acre at le <placeName type="minor">Clerkespath</placeName> by the land of <persName>
                           <forename>Simon</forename> of <surname>Neubolde</surname>
                        </persName>; 1 rood by <placeName type="minor">le Park Weye</placeName> by the land of <persName>John of D<supplied>aventry</supplied>
                        </persName>. In the south field of Drayton
<pb n="67"/>
   5 roods under <placeName type="minor">Stepenhulle</placeName> by the land of <persName>
                           <forename>Geoffrey</forename> le <surname>porter</surname> of <placeName role="person" key="place_108013">Drayton</placeName>
                        </persName>; ½ acre at <placeName type="minor">le Grouesithe</placeName> under <placeName type="minor">le Lede</placeName> by the land of <persName>
                           <forename>William</forename> 
                           <surname>Gemme</surname>
                        </persName>, and in the north field of Drayton ½ acre over <placeName type="minor">Langedone</placeName> by the land of the same <persName>
                           <forename>William</forename> 
                           <surname>Gemme</surname>
                        </persName>. Given at <placeName role="date" key="place_108012">D<supplied>aventry</supplied>
                        </placeName>.
   Witnesses: <persName>
                           <forename>John</forename> 
                           <surname>Bachous</surname>
                        </persName>, 
   <persName>
                           <forename>William</forename> de <surname>aula</surname>
                        </persName>,
   <persName>
                           <forename>William</forename> de <surname>Lauda</surname> of <placeName role="person" key="place_108012">D<supplied>aventry</supplied>
                           </placeName>
                        </persName>, 
   <persName>
                           <forename>Geoffrey</forename> le <surname>porter</surname>
                        </persName>, 
   <persName>
                           <forename>John</forename> le <surname>Wereur</surname> of <placeName role="person" key="place_108013">Drayton</placeName>
                        </persName>. 
   <origDate when="1348-11-12">
                           <supplied>12 Nov. 1348.</supplied>
                        </origDate>
                     </p>
